## Key Files

| What | Where |
|------|-------|
| Session state | `.context/handover/[workstation].md` |
| Glossary | `.context/glossary.md` |
| Module inventory | `.context/substrate.md` |
| Coding rules | `.context/ai-rules.md` |

## Workflow

```
/flow-resume     -> Start session (loads handover state)
/flow-start <#>  -> Pick up issue
/flow-ship       -> Commit + PR to main
/flow-handover   -> End session (saves handover state)
```

## AI Usage

| Task | Read First |
|------|------------|
| Any code change | `.context/ai-rules.md` |
| Domain terms | `.context/glossary.md` |
| Module overview | `.context/substrate.md` |
| Architecture decisions | `.context/architecture/decisions/` |
